name: Sebelas Rumah: 11 Stories of Erasure
description: Digital Collage / 2000x1250 px / 2017 /  "11 Rumah : 11 Stories of Erasure" is a reflection that captures a fleeting moment through Kampung Bharu’s rapid change. Evoking the impending un-mooring and relocation of eleven traditional ‘kampung’ houses of Kampung Bharu, examining the idea of memory and nature of erasure of a village in the contemporary urban condition.
